<main id="content" class="content"> <header> <h1 class="title">Be the Body of Christ</h1>
 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">Sep 12, 2017 00:00</p>
</header> <p>
We are the Body of Christ.
</p>

 <p>
He cannot go where <br></br>
we refuse to tread, <br></br>
speak what we <br></br>
refuse to say, <br></br>
or share what <br></br>
we refuse to give.
</p>

 <p>
May we be the <br></br>
instruments of <br></br>
his love and grace.
</p>

 <p>
 <i>Amen</i>
</p>


